<page>
   <topic>UI_MODELESS_DLG_CLOSE Function</topic>
    <description>Close an named modeless dialog box, returns .T. if dialog was found, .f. if dialog is not open.</description>

   <syntax>L UI_MODELESS_DLG_CLOSE(C title)</syntax>
   <arguments>
     <argument>
         <name>title</name>
         <description>The title of the dialog.</description>
     </argument>
   </arguments>
     <discussion>
The UI_MODELESS_DLG_CLOSE() function closes a modeless dialog box.
   </discussion>
  
   <sections>
       <section><title>Example</title>
            <description>This example creates a modeless dialog box, then closes it.</description>
            <example><![CDATA[
ui_modeless_dlg_box("Visible Xdialog",<<%dlg%
<20,3Click Here>
%dlg%)
ui_modeless_dlg_close("Visible Xdialog")

]]></example>
       </section>
   </sections>
